## How to Run the App

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Asi-Web/JAWG-Contacts.git
cd JAWG-Contacts
```

2. Make sure Flask is installed:

```bash
pip install flask
```

3. Run the application:

```bash
python app.py
```

4. Open your browser and go to:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:5050/
```

## How to Use the App

1. Open the home page.
2. Register a new account.
3. Log in with your account.
4. View the dashboard.
5. Add a contact.
6. Edit or delete contacts as needed.
7. Log out when finished.

