## Project Idea and Purpose

JAWG Contacts is a simple web-based contact manager for keeping track of people and organizations connected to internship and professional work.

The purpose of this project is to create an application that allows a user to store and manage professional contacts in one place. Important details may include a contact’s name, organization, role, email address, and a short note about the connection.

